println("")

println("[9] BREAKTHROUGH PATH (per @D d2)")
println("  P1 1-point DSC: lid+tet+capric 0.4:0.4:0.2, $200-500, 1 day -> validates eutectic prediction")
println("  P2 1-point Franz cell ion-pair: lid+LA vs lid base, $500-1000 -> validates K_sc shift")
println("  P3 leverage Pliaglis patent WO2004103260A2 (Adams) -> ternary already covered IP; need novel ratio")
println("  P4 fold N6-C into hexa-LAC v2 spec (n6_v2.hexa) AFTER P1+P2 PASS -> 🟠 -> 🟡")
println("")

println("=== verdict: N6 is a STEADY-STATE FLUX MULTIPLIER (NOT onset accelerator) ===")
println("=== Candidate C (lid+tet+capric+ion-pair) stacks 6x flux over hexa-LAC v1 ===")
